## Common Patterns

### Loading States
```tsx
if (data === undefined) {
  return (
    <div className="flex items-center justify-center p-8">
      <div className="animate-spin rounded-full h-8 w-8 border-b-2 border-tron-cyan" />
    </div>
  );
}
```

### Empty States
```tsx
if (data.length === 0) {
  return (
    <div className="text-center py-12 text-tron-gray">
      <p>No items found</p>
    </div>
  );
}
```

### Buttons
```tsx
// Primary action
<button className="px-4 py-2 bg-tron-cyan/20 border border-tron-cyan/50 rounded-lg text-tron-cyan hover:bg-tron-cyan/30 transition-colors">
  Primary Action
</button>

// Secondary/subtle
<button className="px-4 py-2 bg-tron-bg-card border border-tron-cyan/20 rounded-lg text-tron-gray hover:text-tron-cyan hover:border-tron-cyan/40 transition-colors">
  Secondary
</button>
```

### Forms
```tsx
<input
  type="text"
  className="w-full px-3 py-2 bg-tron-bg-card border border-tron-cyan/20 rounded-lg text-tron-white placeholder-tron-muted focus:border-tron-cyan/50 focus:outline-none"
  placeholder="Enter value..."
/>
```

